          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Corrections were applied to the data for elastic",
                "energy loss, multiple scattering, finite detector",
                "size, variation of the beam energy and intensity with",
                "angle, finite-source detector spacing, and fission",
                "effects. The fission correction was determined by",
                "first calibrating the detection efficiency for",
                "fission neutrons at each detector bias by using the",
                "spontaneous fissions from Pu240, and then measuring the",
                " induced fission rate by means of a detector bias set",
                "above the initial neutron energy but below the upper",
                "energy limit of the fission spectrum."
              ]
            }
          ],
